    "data": [
      {
        "title_zh": "技术要求",
        "title_en": "",
        "type": "list",
        "content": "<ul><li>带★要求，为产品重要和关键特性</li><li>引出线不能断开，绝缘层和线芯不能损伤</li><li>定子引出线参照GB/T 7345-2008要求</li><li>对于定子三相线，每根引出线应能承受9.0N的拉力</li></ul>",
        "content_en": "<ul><li>Key feature marked ★</li><li>No lead break; no insul./core damage</li><li>Stator leadsperGB/T 7345-2008requirements</li><li></li></ul>",
        "text": "技术要求Technicalrequirements:\n1、带★要求，为产品重要和关键特性\nRequirements marked with ★ indicate important and\ncriticalfeatures oftheproduct\n2、引出线不能断开，绝缘层和线芯不能损伤\nThe outgoing line cannot be disconnected,and the\ninsulation layer and wire core cannot be damaged\n3、定子引出线参照GB/T7345-2008要求\nThe stator outgoing line shall comply with the\nrequirementsofGB/T7345-2008\n4、对于定子三相线，每根引出线应能承受9.0N的拉力\nFor stator three-phase wires, each lead out wire\nshould be able to withstand atensile force of 9.ON",
